## Attribution

EverythingSales Claude Code (ESCC) adapts machinery and architectural patterns
from Everything Claude Code (ECC) — https://github.com/affaan-m/ECC — which is
licensed MIT, Copyright (c) Affaan Mustafa.

ESCC reverses ECC's `skill-adaptation-policy`: rather than vendoring upstream
surfaces wholesale, ESCC adapts the *ideas* into sales-native components and
credits the upstream source. Files ported or adapted from ECC carry an
attribution header pointing back to the originating module. The `ECC_*`
environment-variable surface is mirrored as `ESCC_*` with the same names and
defaults.
